item.title: 254: Linux Laptops, Fedora, DreamWorks Open Source, LXQt Desktop & more Linux news
item.description: February seems to be a really big month for desktop environment news because KDE Plasma is almost upon us with the release next week. GNOME has announced the beta release of GNOME 46. LXQt has dropped some big news that LXQt 2.0 is on its way. Feed: https://tuxdigital.com/feed/thisweekinlinux-mp3
